Index entries for sequences related to matroids
formula: T(n,2) = -n + Sum_{k = 1..n} p(k) for n >= 2, where p(k) = A000041(k). [Dukes (2004), Theorem 2.1.] (End)
xref: Columns include (truncated versions of) A000012 (k=0), A000027 (k=1), A058682 (k=2), A058693 (k=3).
